Deji Elumoye in Abuja President Muhammadu Buhari will broadcast to the nation on Sunday, June 12, 2022, at 7am as part of activities to commemorate this year’s Democracy Day.The Media Adviser to the President, Femi Adesina, in a release issued Saturday, advised television, radio stations, and other electronic media outlets to hook up to the network services of the Nigerian Television Authority and Radio Nigeria for the broadcast.